- Turn It On Again: The Hits (Genesis): This is a solid hits compilation for Genesis, featuring notable tracks (for example Invisible Touch, Land of Confusion, Turn It On Again, I Can’t Dance). Genesis’s catalogue spans progressive and pop-rock phases; many tracks are excellent but often appeal more to listeners who follow the band’s evolution or appreciate longer, more progressive arrangements.
